{
  "texts": [
    "The developed AH-CNN-LSTM and AH-CNN-Res-LSTM models employed the developed IYSGA for parameter optimization.",
    "Since this algorithm provides a crucial part in the developed human motion intention prediction process, the performance investigation of this algorithm is significant.",
    "The performance measures such as accuracy, sensitivity, FM, MK, and DOR are validated.",
    "From the experiments, the accuracy of the IYSGA is enhanced by 6.93% of Jaya, 3.21% of BCO, 4.29% of DO, and 1.17% of POA respectively.",
    "From this experiment, it has been elucidated that the designed IYSGA attained relatively more accurate solutions than the existing algorithms."
  ]
}